Package: farr
Title: Computation of the Fraction of Attributable Risk for Records
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides methods to compute 
    the Fraction of Attributable Risk for Records as described in 
    Naveau, P., Ribes, A., Zwiers, F., Hannart, A., Tuel, A., & Yiou, P.
    Revising return periods for record events in a climate event attribution context.
    J. Clim., 2018.}, \url{https://doi.org/10.1175/JCLI-D-16-0752.1}.
